   review:"Pixel 10 Pro raises the computational photography bar yet again. Tensor G5, designed entirely in-house by Google, runs Gemini Ultra models fully on-device for the first time \u2014 no cloud required. Night Sight 3.0 captures usable photos in near-darkness, while Video Unblur salvages shaky handheld footage in post. Satellite SOS messaging adds genuine peace of mind for outdoor users. The 5000mAh battery finally gives Pixel users all-day confidence without rationing. Seven years of updates to 2032 make this the most future-proof Android on the market.",
