   review:"Xiaomi 15 Ultra is the undisputed camera phone champion of 2025. The world-first variable aperture 200MP sensor \u2014 borrowed from Huawei's breakthrough Pura 70 Pro technology but dramatically improved \u2014 offers real optical depth-of-field control from f/1.4 to f/4.0, letting you shoot bokeh that rivals a full-frame camera. Four Leica Summilux lenses covering ultrawide, 3x, and 5x periscope complete a camera system that has no rival. At $1,399 it costs the same as the Xiaomi 14 Ultra before it but delivers dramatically more. Snapdragon 8 Elite and a 6000mAh battery with 90W/80W charging make sure the rest of the phone matches the camera ambitions.",
